name: Gloria Guida (Textual Inversion)
description:
Gloria Guida

She is one of the main interpreters of the Italian sexy comedies of the seventies, as well as other films mainly with an erotic background. All the images of Gloria that I have used come from her period of activity which goes from 1974 (when she was 19 years old) to 1979.

This first version was trained by request of settima_ai on a dataset of 59 images, mostly from 70's magazine scans and film stills, enhanced with Photo AI than manually cropped to fit 512x512 (since A1111 TI training doesn't have buckets), with WD14 captions manually edited.

In future versions I hope to be able to get better photographic material. In some of the images used, Gloria is completely naked, but is shot from behind. However, her beauty has always been elegant and never obscene. In Italy they had given her the nickname of "queen of showers", together with the equally famous and beautiful actress Edwige Fenech.
